replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 送之前唔打電話<br />\n2. 送唔到之後打比個客，但個係無來電，我不嬲都唔聽133<br />\n3. 打電話上去入完運單編號，自動cut線，試左3次都係咁<br />\n<br />\n點解跨國企業都咁垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2/3都未試過<br />\n3打去係有人接聽唔知點樣&ldquo;入&ldquo;個tracking我都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e4093187feacc631610dc1908af4c972e30ac9","tid":163751,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"DHL好喎<br />\nSF先差 態度差不負責任"},{"pid":"da17199722360c55c85eeed2ecd2fc158efaf412","tid":163751,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:05:26.000Z","msg":"人柒俾人欺"},{"pid":"0215e2798b9f68a8389d6b4a53aea1b640755586","tid":163751,"uid":29075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"OP 打嗰個咩電話嚟<br />\n24003388 直接有人聽喎<br />\n未試過要入冧把"},{"pid":"3bfa0870a815bcc8f696ec9bb1aa01c852b2058d","tid":163751,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"同樣DHL 送<br />\n1. 送之前無電話<br />\n2. 送唔到無電話<br />\n3. 由頭到尾都唔知送左未就彈左返去俾寄件條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知DHL 問題定送發貨條友無放我電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f851620e53f7c43cd2ed46ec80896dc3dcc0414","tid":163751,"uid":61423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"其實DHL送貨算係咁wor<br />\n之前幾次都係有人打黎我無聽到 但佢會照上門<br />\n同埋都算快<br />\n不過之前有次我好急要送件貨去英國 <br />\n打去DHL問好曬尺寸收費 電話confirm左佢搵人上門收件 即時現金比錢 都成千蚊多少少<br />\n咁好啦 之後件貨都好快送到英國果邊 <br />\n跟住過多個禮拜dhl打黎同我講件貨照左size <br />\n要charge多我8百幾 即係total成2000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗2000蚊我自己搭飛機帶埋過去唔好<br />\n<br />\n第一 果時同佢confirm曬size收費先<br />\n第二 佢搵人上黎收件收錢時check又無問題<br />\n第三 就算佢收件返去發現size超左 都好應該打返比同我講返要收返差價先再決定係咪照寄 佢係完全無同我提過就send左件貨去屈9我比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f0bbf63157384abfa2eacecfc938c9833afb30","tid":163751,"uid":20720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T15:26:50.000Z","msg":"dhl有時入左大廈門口掉低張卡入信箱話你屋企冇人<br />\n其實屋企有人佢懶到唔上門"},{"pid":"16ee767ce50645b210a6b16e165a00e0d3ad1d6a","tid":163751,"uid":35920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"我DHL左好多次<br />\n貴野/重野/要簽名個類既急件又快又好態度<br />\n平少少個啲 即係搵阿叔送個啲就差到屎咁<br />\n有時佢叫郵局代送我反而仲開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448d37f61198c59f205ffd5f587ccf02ada79197","tid":163751,"uid":63160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:42:30.000Z","msg":"約左今日6-10點送，岩岩沖緊涼無聴到電話，之後即刻打比佢，點撚知佢話無人聽走左，就快就走咁我約時間把撚呀"},{"pid":"2e23cfe5fd9dbdad2c1d8d7b93caf46b3ded8ae1","tid":163751,"uid":63160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 送之前唔打電話<br />\n2. 送唔到之後打比個客，但個係無來電，我不嬲都唔聽133<br />\n3. 打電話上去入完運單編號，自動cut線，試左3次都係咁<br />\n<br />\n點解跨國企業都咁垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2/3都未試過<br />\n3打去係有人接聽唔知點樣&ldquo;入&ldquo;個tracking我都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最on9我入完個track code, 客服叫我講多次，心諗個system唔係咁廢呀"},{"pid":"ec5c84d45a0ed7dcf23acc32d4a7d2ba39412046","tid":163751,"uid":63160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:51:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔聽133正戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n成日比人打嚟搵陳小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6583101923167b8efce7e46c3820f01d4a5c8b93","tid":163751,"uid":3193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:53:20.000Z","msg":"送到先打電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889a4b5d7bf4bd552182ee998695129c14350678","tid":163751,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:55:36.000Z","msg":"係咪蘋果件呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"