r<br />\n之前幾次都係有人打黎我無聽到 但佢會照上門<br />\n同埋都算快<br />\n不過之前有次我好急要送件貨去英國 <br />\n打去DHL問好曬尺寸收費 電話confirm左佢搵人上門收件 即時現金比錢 都成千蚊多少少<br />\n咁好啦 之後件貨都好快送到英國果邊 <br />\n跟住過多個禮拜dhl打黎同我講件貨照左size <br />\n要charge多我8百幾 即係total成2000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗2000蚊我自己搭飛機帶埋過去唔好<br />\n<br />\n第一 果時同佢confirm曬size收費先<br />\n第二 佢搵人上黎收件收錢時check又無問題<br />\n第三 就算佢收件返去發現size超左 都好應該打返比同我講返要收返差價先再決定係咪照寄 佢係完全無同我提過就send左件貨去屈9我比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你最後點？</blockquote><br />\n第一時間問清楚佢點計多800幾差價<br />\n佢話要通知acct果邊check個數點計出黎<br />\n之後佢acct打黎 我咁岩返工無聽 佢夠膽死當我agree左比錢 直接叫人上門搵我收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住佢再搵acct call我又miss call (真係miss唔係特登) 又當多次我agree比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢cs嘈左一輪 最後無再追我到依家"},{"pid":"12a3d585dfc4b2f46e8bc6235384a435d397de83","tid":163751,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T14:45:59.000Z","msg":"上網改時間好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網改好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9bae7cf873cf79d6a05cf322ad11246dabad73","tid":163751,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T14:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係喎<br />\n只要track到件包裹到咗香港<br />\n就可以打去叫佢指定咩時間送<br />\n我覺得好撚方便喎<br />\n<br />\n第三點我真係未試過</blockquote><br />\n試過明明指定9:30-13:00送<br />\nDHL 個人9點正就送黎<br />\n黎之前都無個電話<br />\n搞到差d miss 左</blockquote><br />\n最憎啲送貨佬早到仲要嫌你遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過兩次 非dhl"},{"pid":"d53dfcbe28032702a3fca8f2672fa0dcbceb855f","tid":163751,"uid":20766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:25:49.000Z","msg":"宅急便先係西中之霸"},{"pid":"ff4b090025d5ed1b32ed1a577876e625a1746d22","tid":163751,"uid":14167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:33:00.000Z","msg":"DHL好似會留卡架啵"},{"pid":"30a2508fec68b6722857c818bde73dca1aef85c6","tid":163751,"uid":92814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"之前博客來訂野，送之前冇比電話，唔係屋企，入左張卡係信箱，打電話去即晚安排送番"},{"pid":"1215f0881ba1de1b0b1fef7d847987c49ae9a3e4","tid":163751,"uid":29063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:38:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係喎<br />\n只要track到件包裹到咗香港<br />\n就可以打去叫佢指定咩時間送<br />\n我覺得好撚方便喎<br />\n<br />\n第三點我真係未試過</blockquote><br />\n試過明明指定9:30-13:00送<br />\nDHL 個人9點正就送黎<br />\n黎之前都無個電話<br />\n搞到差d miss 左</blockquote><br />\n我試過送bno嚟<br />\n明明我全日係屋企，打個電話嚟我都未聽得切就收線<br />\n轉頭打去佢話嚟過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果打去cs改時間<br />\n第二次費事再miss，打多次confrim, 呢個cs就同我講上一手改錯日子，改左下星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到佢真係朝早送嚟，我啱啱係樓下商場食緊早餐，我食到一半出去攞，佢跳落車交低件野就跳返上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d6d07132309ca84f627c09b6d15c864ab04b63","tid":163751,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"一面倒留言話dhl服務好，樓主係咪用左其他喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9123f5864bafc5203f19bfa612bf501a009b88fd","tid":163751,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:47:48.000Z","msg":"DHL出名垃圾"},{"pid":"9a832e04d9bbfc32e4adbd56f8624410c15c4c5e","tid":163751,"uid":5724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:55:38.000Z","msg":"送貨佬問題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n送我個附近個呀叔送之前一定會打電話，有時無聽仲會留言<br />\n如果少貨無人聽都會黎左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係每次拍門拍兩下就走，有時未開得切門就走左搞到要喺走廊叫佢返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08b5cfdea847adab60a2fcad88a0a6def7b48d7","tid":163751,"uid":742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/763SQC9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F763SQC9.jpg&h=9599ad6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87ad3af43b7337f9f1c62665e80c3fb2be3cb44d","tid":163751,"uid":8435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:30:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>DHL先好 送上黎會打電話<br />\n去到屋企樓下先臨時改地址送去第二到又肯<br />\n屋企無人 book完時間 第二日已經即刻收到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">其實我覺得睇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過有次唔喺香港，屋企又無人收<br />\n我阿媽驚太耐份件會彈返轉頭就幫我打去dhl約再送<br />\n約咗喺某百貨公司門口收件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d3bea95cd8486a88a60f784f519655ee200eab","tid":163751,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:32:09.000Z","msg":"US送個件黎HK送成個月<br />\n送前又係冇電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d446032d07244cb0c776e026c749993d970f512","tid":163751,"uid":43808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"淨係試過寄急件去英國，第二日就到英國，覺得好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n收件情況就唔知啦"}]}